Workflow for snapshot Cycle
1) Setup Job
2) Initialize containers
3) Checkout Branch
4) Build and publish Snapshot Artifacts
5) Sonarqube Scan
6) Veracode Scan
7) Validate Artifacts
8) Build snapshot event payload
9) Build Relese Artifact Event Payload
10) Clean up Runner workspace
12) Post checkout Branch
13) Stop Containers
14) Compelte job
